HTTP Post Requests
Useful link - 'requests' module documentation
https://requests.readthedocs.io/en/latest/api/

Types of methods:
get - requests.get()
Retrieve info from a site

post - requests.put()
Post info on a site
Ex: Tweet something on Twitter

put - requests.put()
Update a piece of data on an external service
Ex: Update some values in a spreadsheet

delete - requests.delete()
Delete a piece of data on an external service

Check other features in the requests module by checking the documentation link above


